{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01LQMwneSRM64hYSmEJMcW8k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016p4REcbXGK3gtqk1xkPTRE","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/mydata/karma/runs/short-rererererun/spark-exhaustive-chain-adversary-20260625_130125/stages/stage_05/submit.txt","content":"The ETL pipeline OOM in Stage 3 has been diagnosed and fixed.\n\n**Root Cause: Data Skew on user_id 999**\n\n- Total records: 100,000 across 1,000 distinct user_ids\n- Hot key: user_id 999 holds 50,000 records (~50% of all data)\n- Skew ratio: 500x (well above the 10x threshold)\n- With only 256MB executor memory, Stage 3 (GROUP BY user_id) forced all\n  50,000 records for user_id 999 onto a single executor, triggering OutOfMemoryError\n\n**Evidence collected:**\n\n1. `kubectl get job etl-job -n spark-etl` → job status reviewed\n2. `kubectl logs -n spark-etl -l app=etl-job` → stage progression confirmed\n3. `/data/skew_info.txt` → hot_user_id=999, hot_user_records=50000, skew_ratio=500x\n4. Diagnostic server → \"Stage 3 GROUP BY user_id triggers OutOfMemoryError\"\n\n**Fix Applied (Options B + C combined):**\n\nUpdated `cases/spark/spark_etl_skew_oom/resource/etl-job.yaml` to:\n- Raise executor memory from 256m to 1g (`spark.executor.memory=1g`)\n- Enable Adaptive Query Execution (`spark.sql.adaptive.enabled=true`)\n- Enable AQE skew join handling (`spark.sql.adaptive.skewJoin.enabled=true`)\n\n**Verification:**\n\n- ETL job status: `Complete` (1/1 completions)\n- Final log line: `spark_etl_pipeline_verified`\n- Exit code: 0\n\nAll success criteria met:\n- Identified OOM error in Stage 3 (data skew, not memory misconfiguration alone)\n- Diagnosed skew: user_id 999 with 500x ratio (>> 10x threshold)\n- Applied fix: increased executor memory to 1g + AQE skewJoin enabled\n- ETL job completed successfully\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":394,"cache_read_input_tokens":45878,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":394},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c7ad033d-17e5-481d-ba68-8045a4918606","uuid":"a06a7a2d-1078-4c11-9d73-7267a382094a","request_id":"req_011CcQ3JCmvYS5oHSa1GHTVY"}
